videos.description: Mark Walton run for 80 yds for a TD
videos.headline: Miami breaks 80 yard TD run on first play from scrimmage

videos.description: Brad Kaaya pass complete to David Njoku for 9 yds for a TD
videos.headline: B. Kaaya pass,to D. Njoku for 9 yds for a TD

videos.description: Miami RB Mark Walton runs through a tackle and sprints for an 80-yard touchdown on the first play of the game against Appalachian State.
videos.headline: Miami bursts for long TD on first play

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Miami bursts for long TD on first play) 2016/09/17 ESHEET

videos.description: Miami QB Brad Kaaya throws a 55-yard touchdown pass to Stacy Coley, extending Miami's lead over Appalachian State.
videos.headline: Kaaya finds wide open Coley for 55-yard TD

videos.description: Miami WR Braxton Berrios comes down with a diving catch next to the sidelines for a 13 yard gain and a first down.
videos.headline: Miami WR Berrios makes great diving catch on tip toes

videos.description: Miami QB Brad Kaaya finds Stacy Coley again for an 8-yard touchdown giving the Hurricanes a 38-10 lead over Appalachian State.
videos.headline: Kaaya's third TD pass puts game out of reach

videos.description: Mark Walton puts an exclamation point on the game for Miami with a 10-yard run and diving over a pair of defenders to find the end zone, increasing the Hurricanes' lead to 45-10.
videos.headline: Walton leaps and somersaults into the end zone
